--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages coreutils.

A set of basic GNU tools commonly used in shell scripts.

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: coreutils
       coreutils_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: coreutils
       coreutils_state: 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  coreutils_state
    Specify predetermined 'coreutils_state' variable (string).
    Notice: 'coreutils' is a core package and can therefore not be removed.

    Install: 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
    Remove : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'
    Default: 'install'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEPENDENCIES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PACKAGES
  coreutils: >= 8.2
    CentOS, RedHat, Gentoo

ROLES

VARIABLES

